7.0.0.name: wordpress/easy-csv-importer-2
7.0.0.description: Import posts, comments, custom fields and more from any CSV file. This is the first truly easy importer plugin for Wordpress. Easy CSV Importer imports data to a project database table where we can work with the data. Then we design our template in the WYSIWYG editor and click a button to create posts. The premium edition is also super easy while still deliver very advanced functionality aimed at professionals.
